  "title": "Cafe Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking to hire a motivated and team player to join our family as Cafe Supervisor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job scope includes (and is not limited to):</p>\n<p>- in charge of stock take and ordering</p>\n<p>- training of new servers</p>\n<p>- oversee day-to-day cafe operation</p>\n<p>- table service; manage complaints</p>\n<p>- cashiering</p>\n<p>- oversee cleanliness and order of cafe</p>\n<p>- preparation of coffee, other beverages and desserts</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>--------</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Flexible timing, available to work weekends</p>\n<p>- Shift work available</p>\n<p>- Meals provided</p>\n<p>- Cafe is 8 mins walk from Farrer Park MRT, Lavender MRT, Jalan Besar MRT stations.</p>",
